Interface TreeItem

All Known Implementing Classes:
ApplicationType, ApplicationTypeGroup, Division, Estimate, IndustrySector, IndustrySectorGroup, Organization, PiHistoryCategory, PiHistoryEntry, ProjectLife, ReportItem, ReportMilestone, ReportPhase, Solution, UseCase, UseCasePack
public interface TreeItem

This interface provides the functionality for entities to be represented in a hierarchical form.
Entities which has a parent->children relationship should implement this interface.
Note: both, parent and child has to implement it

Author:
Gregor Schumm
